TITLE: Episode 55 - Peace Freqs and the Multiverse of Madness
DESCRIPTION: This week, Kim and I are joined by the Peace Freqs. Nick and Lizzie Pecone from former Sounds Like Liberty fame join us to talk about how we are versions of each other from parallel universes, how Nick got the nickname “Three Dicks,” the so-called liberty movement, ginger libertarians, the Libertarian Party, racism, the Civil War, and much more. Join us for a good time among friends.
